Neuropsychological Battery

Source: R/data.R
NEUROBAT.Rd

Neuropsychological Battery data. More information is available at https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Usage

data(NEUROBAT)

Format

A data frame with 17622 observations and 84 variables.

Source

https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Details

  • ORIGPROT character Original study protocol , with options: ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI3, ADNI4

  • COLPROT factor Study protocol of data collection , with levels: ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI3, ADNI4

  • PTID character Participant ID

  • RID numeric Participant roster ID Range value: 1, ..., 10898

  • VISCODE character Visit code

  • VISCODE2 character Translated visit code

  • VISDATE Assessment DATE when present; otherwise Registry EXAMDATE Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • SOURCE character Information Source 1=Participant Visit ; 2=Telephone Call/Video Call Decoded Value: Yes

  • CLOCKCIRC character 1. Approximately circular face

    • ADNI1, ADNI3, ADNI4: 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct

    • ADNIGO, ADNI2: 1=Correct ; 0=Incorrect

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • CLOCKSYM character 2. Symmetry of number placement

    • ADNI1, ADNI3, ADNI4: 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct

    • ADNIGO, ADNI2: 1=Correct ; 0=Incorrect

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • CLOCKNUM character 3. Correctness of numbers

    • ADNI1, ADNI3, ADNI4: 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct

    • ADNIGO, ADNI2: 1=Correct ; 0=Incorrect

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • CLOCKHAND character 4. Presence of the two hands

    • ADNI1, ADNI3, ADNI4: 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct

    • ADNIGO, ADNI2: 1=Correct ; 0=Incorrect

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • CLOCKTIME character 5. Presence of the two hands, set to ten after eleven

    • ADNI1, ADNI3, ADNI4: 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct

    • ADNIGO, ADNI2: 1=Correct ; 0=Incorrect

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • CLOCKSCOR numeric Total Score

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 0..5

    • ADNI3, ADNI4

  • COPYCIRC character 1. Approximately circular face

    • ADNI1: 1=Yes ; 0=No

    • ADNIGO, ADNI2: 1=Correct ; 0=Incorrect

    • ADNI3, ADNI4: 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • COPYSYM character 2. Symmetry of number placement

    • ADNI1: 1=Yes ; 0=No

    • ADNIGO, ADNI2: 1=Correct ; 0=Incorrect

    • ADNI3, ADNI4: 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • COPYNUM character 3. Correctness of numbers

    • ADNI1: 1=Yes ; 0=No

    • ADNIGO, ADNI2: 1=Correct ; 0=Incorrect

    • ADNI3, ADNI4: 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • COPYHAND character 4. Presence of the two hands

    • ADNI1: 1=Yes ; 0=No

    • ADNIGO, ADNI2: 1=Correct ; 0=Incorrect

    • ADNI3, ADNI4: 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • COPYTIME character 5. Presence of the two hands, set to ten after eleven

    • ADNI1: 1=Yes ; 0=No

    • ADNIGO, ADNI2: 1=Correct ; 0=Incorrect

    • ADNI3, ADNI4: 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • COPYSCOR numeric Total Score

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 0..5

    • ADNI3, ADNI4

  • LMSTORY character Which Logical Memory story was used? 1=Anna Thompson ; 2=Greg Fortune Decoded Value: Yes

  • LIMMTOTAL numeric Total Number of Story Units Recalled

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 0..25

    • ADNI3, ADNI4

  • LIMMEND numeric Time Ended (24-hour clock) Range value: 33, ..., 2041

  • AVTOT1 numeric Trial 1 Total

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 0..15

    • ADNI3, ADNI4

  • AVERR1 numeric Total Intrusions Range value: 0, ..., 13

  • AVTOT2 numeric Trial 2 Total

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 0..15

    • ADNI3, ADNI4

  • AVERR2 numeric Total Intrusions Range value: 0, ..., 12

  • AVTOT3 numeric Trial 3 Total

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 0..15

    • ADNI3, ADNI4

  • AVERR3 numeric Total Intrusions Range value: 0, ..., 14

  • AVTOT4 numeric Trial 4 Total

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 0..15

    • ADNI3, ADNI4

  • AVERR4 numeric Total Intrusions Range value: 0, ..., 14

  • AVTOT5 numeric Trial 5 Total

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 0..15

    • ADNI3, ADNI4

  • AVERR5 numeric Total Intrusions Range value: 0, ..., 15

  • AVTOT6 numeric Trial 6 Total

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 0..15

    • ADNI3, ADNI4

  • AVERR6 numeric Total Intrusions Range value: 0, ..., 13

  • AVTOTB numeric List B Total

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 0..15

    • ADNI3, ADNI4

  • AVERRB numeric Total Intrusions Range value: 0, ..., 12

  • AVENDED numeric AVLT Time Trial B Ended Range value: 100, ..., 1925

  • DSPANFOR numeric Forward: Total Correct 0..12

  • DSPANFLTH numeric Forward: Length 3..8

  • DSPANBAC numeric Backward: Total Correct 0..12

  • DSPANBLTH numeric Backward: Length 2..7

  • CATANIMSC numeric Category Fluency (Animals) - Total Correct

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 0..77

    • ADNI3, ADNI4

  • CATANPERS numeric Category Fluency (Animals) - Perseverations

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 0..77

    • ADNI3, ADNI4

  • CATANINTR numeric Category Fluency (Animals) - Intrusions

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 0..77

    • ADNI3, ADNI4

  • CATVEGESC numeric Category Fluency (Vegetables) - Total Correct 0..77

  • CATVGPERS numeric Category Fluency (Vegetables) - Perseverations 0..77

  • CATVGINTR numeric Category Fluency (Vegetables) - Intrusions 0..77

  • TRAASCOR numeric Part A - Time to Complete

    • ADNI1, ADNI2, ADNI3, ADNI4

    • ADNIGO: 1..150

  • TRAAERRCOM numeric Errors of Commission Range value: 0, ..., 24

  • TRAAERROM numeric Errors of Omission

    • ADNI1, ADNI3, ADNI4

    • ADNIGO: 0..24

    • ADNI2: 0..77

  • TRABSCOR numeric Part B - Time to complete

    • ADNI1, ADNI2, ADNI3, ADNI4

    • ADNIGO: 1..300

  • TRABERRCOM numeric Errors of Commission Range value: 0, ..., 25

  • TRABERROM numeric Errors of Omission

    • ADNI1, ADNI2, ADNI3, ADNI4

    • ADNIGO: 0..24

  • DIGITSCOR numeric Total Correct Range value: 0, ..., 83

  • LDELBEGIN numeric Time Began (24-hour clock) Range value: 8, ..., 2112

  • LDELTOTAL numeric Total Number of Story Units Recalled

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 0..25

    • ADNI3, ADNI4

  • LDELCUE character Reminder given?

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 1=Yes ; 0=No

    • ADNI3, ADNI4: 0=No ; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • BNTND character Check here if: 1=Boston Naming Not Done - Spanish speaking Decoded Value: Yes

  • BNTSPONT numeric 1. Total correct without a cue 0..30

  • BNTSTIM numeric 2. Total semantic cues given 0..30

  • BNTCSTIM numeric 3. Total correct with a semantic cue 0..30

  • BNTPHON numeric 4. Total phonemic cues given 0..30

  • BNTCPHON numeric 5. Number of correct responses following a phonemic cue 0..30

  • BNTTOTAL numeric Total Number Correct (1+3) 0..30

  • AVDELBEGAN numeric Time Began (24-hour clock) Range value: 30, ..., 1910

  • AVDEL30MIN numeric 30 Minute Delay Total

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 0..15

    • ADNI3, ADNI4

  • AVDELERR1 numeric Total Intrusions Range value: 0, ..., 30

  • AVDELTOT numeric Recognition Score

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 0..15

    • ADNI3, ADNI4

  • AVDELERR2 numeric Total Intrusions Range value: 0, ..., 17

  • ANARTERR numeric ANART Total Score (Total # of errors)

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 0..50

    • ADNI3, ADNI4

  • ANARTND character Check here if: 1=ANART Not Done - Spanish speaking Decoded Value: Yes

  • ANART character Was ANART conducted? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • MINTSEMCUE numeric MINT Total Correct - with Semantic Cue Range value: 0, ..., 32

  • MINTTOTAL numeric MINT Total Correct (Uncued + Correct with Semantic cue) Range value: 0, ..., 32

  • MINTUNCUED numeric MINT Total Uncued Correct Range value: 0, ..., 32

  • ID numeric Record ID Range value: 6, ..., 187101

  • SITEID numeric Site ID Range value: 1, ..., 941

  • USERDATE User Create Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • USERDATE2 User Last Modify Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • DD_CRF_VERSION_LABEL character CRF Version Label , with options: sc, annual, bl

  • LANGUAGE_CODE character Language Code e=English Decoded Value: Yes

  • HAS_QC_ERROR character Has Quality Check Error 0=Does not have QC error or QC error has been approved ; 1=Has QC error Decoded Value: Yes

  • update_stamp POSIXct: YYY-MM-DD
